'''Didier Kamanzi''', umukinnyi wa filimi mu [[Rwanda]] .  Umwe mu bakinnyi bazwi cyane muri sinema yo mu [[Rwanda]], Kamanzi azwi cyane kubera uruhare muri filime ''Rwasa'', ''Rwassibo'' na ''Catherine'' . 

Usibye gukina, ni n'umukinnyi mu ikipe y'igihugu ya rugby ubumwe bw'u Rwanda . 

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1994 mu [[Uburundi|Burundi]] nk'umwana wa gatatu w'umuryango ufite barumuna be batandatu. Nyuma ya jenoside yo mu [[Rwanda]], yasubiye mu [[Rwanda]] mu 1994 yiga mu mashuri yisumbuye. Yakoze nka bouncer muri club ya nijoro yaho amezi make. 

== Umwuga ==
Mugihe akora nka bouncer muri club nijoro, yabonye igitekerezo cyo kugerageza film. Yagiye muri auditions abona uruhare. 

Muri 2015, yatsindiye igihembo cyumukinnyi witwaye neza mu bihembo bya firime yu [[Rwanda]]. 

